                                            </div>
                                            <div class="tp-case_item-inner-txt">
                                                ※月の使用関数<br />2缶
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="tp-case_item-inner-txt">
                                                =
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="tp-case_item-inner-txt">
                                                月にかかる金額<br />¥12,000
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div
                                            class="tp-case_item-inner-txt-wrapper"
